comments: Bey (DET) and James (LAL) engage and disengage with one another off ball.
Westbrook (LAL) establishes himself in a screening position in Bey's (DET) path and gives him a step to avoid contact.
Horton-Tucker (LAL) lightly brushes Grant's (DET) arm contesting his driving shot attempt and the contact is marginal.
Hayes (DET) legally contests James' (LAL) jump shot attempt.  Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
Horton-Tucker (LAL) moves laterally into Cunningham's (DET) path and the contact affects his SQBR.
James (LAL) places his forearm to Hayes' (DET) side during his drive to the basket and the contact is marginal.
Davis (LAL) closes out on Grant (DET) during the jump shot attempt and the contact that occurs to his lower body is marginal.
Bey (DET) is already in Horton-Tucker's (LAL) path and absorbs the contact.
Monk (LAL) dislodges the ball from Jackson (DET) during his jump shot attempt before incidental contact occurs.
Grant (DET) makes hand on ball contact and dislodges Monk's (LAL) shot attempt before incidental contact occurs.
Replay review of the foul called on Monk (LAL) pursuant to a coach?s challenge was deemed unsuccessful. Monk (LAL) makes contact with Grant's (DET) wrist that affects his shot attempt at the basket.

Jackson (DET) briefly places his hand to Davis' (LAL) front and immediately removes it as he dislodges the ball defending his drive. Jackson (DET) is the last person to touch the ball before it goes out of bounds. The possession is correctly awarded to LAL.
Davis (LAL) establishes himself in a screening position in Jackson's (DET) path and makes marginal contact as they disengage.
Hayes (DET) commits a take foul on Monk (LAL).
Davis (LAL) and Jackson (DET) briefly engage and disengage with another during the screen.
Bey (DET) commits a take foul on James' (LAL).
Davis (LAL) places a resting hand to Hayes' (DET) side during his drive and marginal contact occurs.
Jackson (DET) is already in Monk's (LAL) path and makes marginal contact as they disengage.
Hayes (DET) commits a take foul on Horton-Tucker (LAL).
